God is not the author of evil; but it is the lasting on of the things
made that causes evil to break out on them. And that is why God has
subjected things to changeï¼š for by transmutation the things made are
purged of evil God has one quality, and one alone, the quality of
goodness; and he who is good is neither disdainful nor incapable.
